\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"FAQ\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm whitespace-pre-line\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Q: Has anyone unlocked this legitimately? A: No. Despite six months of community attempts, no player has verified legitimate unlock conditions. Q: Can you trigger it through file editing? A: Yes, but this requires modifying save files and is not considered a legitimate unlock. The game crashes immediately after displaying hex data. Q: Is it related to the Corrupted Data ending? A: The community believes they are the same route, but this is unverified. The Corrupted Data ending may be what the Null Route was intended to unlock.\\\"}]]}]\\n9:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Related Content\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L11\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/endings/corrupted-data\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Related Ending\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Corrupted Data →\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\\\",\\\"chi\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"ldren\\\":\\\"The unverified ending investigation\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L11\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/theories\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-4 hover:border-primary